  - is_modified=True + mod_val >= 2000 → modified_vehicle
  - is_salvage ou is_rebuilt = True    → salvage_or_rebuilt
  - has_gap_in_coverage = True         → gap_in_coverage
  - years_prior_insurance = 0          → gap_in_coverage
  - has_foreign_driving_experience     → foreign_experience
  - commercial_use_description non vide → commercial_use_borderline

REGLE SPECIALE : is_excluded=True → accidents/convictions NE COMPTENT PAS

STATUTS EXCEL :
  APPROUVE / VERIFICATION_HUMAINE / REFUSE

